Answer these honey nut cereal bars! Sarah's Tip of the Day When lining your cake pan with parchment, allow at least an inch of overhang on two sides so you can easily lift your treats out once they've set. STEP 2 Combine butter, sugar, honey, salt, and cinnamon in a medium saucepan. Bring to a boil, stirring constantly. Continue to boil for 1 to 2 minutes, then immediately remove from heat.
